title: 820-3115 missing pm_slp_s4_L
message: this is my personal machine. coffee was spilled on it about 18 months ago with no major corrosion.  Just died on me today.  I found that pp5_s5_LDO was missing and with a little more troublshooting found no PM-SLP-S4_L

title: 820-3115 missing pm_slp_s4_L
message: You have to have 5V_S5 before you get PM_SLP_S4_L. Green light present? PPBUS voltage? VRTC voltage? Voltage on PP5V_S5 and PP3V3_S5?

title: 820-3115 missing pm_slp_s4_L
message: well, it's working now, it appears to have fixed itself.  not the first time probing around got the fan spinning again.
